BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p>The summer heat is coming back\, and AroSpAce wants to go picknicking!<br/>We will meet at 19:00 at the youth-centre\, and will then leave from there together at 19:30 towards Isar to find a cozy place for us.  Feel free to bring a picnic blanket\, your own snacks\, and some games. As is will be quite warm that day please also bring enough to drink and appropriate sun protection.</p><p>For all that want to join late we will post our location into our Telegram Channel\, or you can write us <a id="1677" linktype="page">here</a>.</p><p><i>AroSpAce is a group for teens and young adults between 14 and 27\, who identify themselves with the aromantic and/or the asexual spectrum (including Demi-\, Grey-\, etc.). If you identify with either or both of these spectra or are questioning you are very welcome to join our meetings.</i></p><p><i>Unfortunately our youth centre is not accessible. Should you have accessibility needs\, please write us at arospace[at]diversity-muenchen.de . Maybe we can find a solution.</i></p>\n\n(Error: The event had no end date)
DURATION:PT2H57M
LOCATION:diversity Jugendzentrum\, Blumenstraße 11\, 80331\, München
DTSTART:20250812T170000Z
SUMMARY:AroSpAce: Isar-Picknick
UID:5371ce48-08d6-4017-9907-49b98dbdfba4@5371.org
END:VEVENT
